      "code": "if (SSF2API.isReady()) {\n\tself.self = /* ? */;\n\tself.playsound = SSF2API.random();\n\tself.audio = self.self.getGlobalVariable(\"audio\");\n\tself.self.swapDepthsWithGrabbedOpponent(true);\n}\nreturn;",
